wiki.content: “COCAINE NOSE” is the 20th song on Playboi Carti's long awaited album "MUSIC". The song was previewed for the first time at Rolling Loud on December 15, 2024. This track showcases an aggressive, rage-infused, rap-rock instrumental, which was produced by F1LTHY, 100yrd, & Brak3. The track also features a raspier voice by Playboi Carti, which was also featured in the intro track, "POP OUT". The song delves into themes of hedonism, drug culture, and the extravagant lifestyle that accompanies fame, characterized by a repetitive and hypnotic chorus that emphasizes indulgence and excess.
